  "detailed_description": "Oh no! The cats have gotten loose - and it's up to our hero, Bob the Yeti, to collect them all!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile trying to rescue all the lost felines, Bob must face upcoming dangers such as falling platforms, rolling snowballs and slippy ice bricks - not to mention some of the unleashed cats themselves! Is Bob up to the challenge?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nInspired by the classic platformers from the past decades, Bob's Cat Challenge offers an exciting 3D adventure for players of all ages!",
